snippet.title: inbento - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Open your cookbook, grab a lunchbox, and start preparing exceptional bento meals in over 100 amazing puzzles. Master the mechanics, follow the hand-crafted recipes, and beat all the bonus stages in this culinary logic game starring a cute family of cats. With so much stress around, let's PAWS for a second and relax with a few rounds of inbento - OUT NOW on Nintendo Switch!

Available Now: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/inbento-switch/
